      "span_text": "The success of CAPTCHA's (von Ahn et al. 2003) shows that it is possible to automatically generate images that are easy for people to interpret and hard for computers; however, that is an unusual case. [CITATION_1] propose to build a system that uses a world model and a linguistic model to generate simple narratives in commonsense domains."
